FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a nuclear fuel bundle with parts broken out and in cross-section;


FIG. 2 is a schematic representation of a cross-section or lattice of a nuclear fuel bundle;


FIG. 3A is a cross-sectional view with parts broken out of a fuel rod illustrating stacked fuel pellets within the fuel rods according to the prior art;


FIG. 3B is a view similar to FIG. 3A illustrating a shortened length of fuel in an edge fuel rod according to the present invention;


FIG. 4A is a view similar to FIG. 3A illustrating conventional spacing between the fuel pellets within a fuel rod and the interior surface of the rod; and


FIG. 4B is a view similar to FIG. 4A illustrating reduced diameter pellets in an edge fuel rod in accordance with the present invention.
